<br>
1) If I lev and run over to the island, bolt one of the spectres, can they be single pulled ?<br>
<br>
2) Can they be soloed at 36 with 195int ?<br>
<br>
Thanks.  Whatever other information you can contribute is most welcome <p><br><br><strong>Goramon Coldfire</strong> [Unbroken Circle of Valor]<br>
