Vazaelle<br><br>

Those that can't, summon pets.  Those that can, blow shit up. =)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uheihache.showPublicProfile?language=EN>heihache</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/1/01 12:28:12 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.iquest.net/~jynx25/me.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spectres in Oasis... single pulls ?</span><hr size=1> You'll be able to solo a single pull at 36, but the hard part is getting a single pull.  Most pulls will be 2.  If that is the case, just BOF them, kill one, and zone the other.  That's the only way I know of.  Also, some will be even or maybe even yellow to you.  Be carefull with them, they will kill you.  Try to get blues only and you should be ok.  If you want to get revenge on something, I suggest hitting Rathe Mountians and teaching the HG's a lesson <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><a href=#><img src=http://members.iquest.net/~jynx25/robe.jpg border=0></a>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugoramon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goramon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/1/01 12:58:44 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spectres in Oasis... single pulls ?</span><hr size=1> Heh, i've been in rathe alot lately =P<br>
