Those that can't, summon pets.  Those that can, blow shit up. =)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=branaman>Branaman</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/1/01 2:31:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spectres in Oasis... single pulls ?</span><hr size=1> Hmm i need 3 conflags = 1800 dmg for specters. And i use BoF.<br>
<br>
Just calculate your dmg output and the mana needed for BoF on a full bar of mana.<br>
<br>
Single pulling is possible if you stay in the water and pull with flux staff. usually you get one, but it can be 2. If 2, round them up close in the water by running around, then go ashore and BoF them both. Kill one and zone into S ro. The other will wander off and gives a whole new generation of lower level players the feeling you have right now.  <p>Branaman Starbinder <Hated Ones > <BR>
48th Dark Elf Wizard on Prexus</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uspace78.showPublicProfile?language=EN>space78</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/2/01 9:35:37 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spectres in Oasis... single pulls ?</span><hr size=1> i was never able to successfully break a camp or single pull until lvl 48, then i could pull one out of a tight grp of 4 without agroing the others, but at 48 they start greening out a bit <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=british>British</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/2/01 12:16:58 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spectres in Oasis... single pulls ?</span><hr size=1> There are two of them on the island that can be single-pulled if you get the angle right.  If memory serves me correctly, the ones on the southwest and northwest corner can be pulled in this fashion.  <br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=branaman>Branaman</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/3/01 12:32:20 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spectres in Oasis... single pulls ?</span><hr size=1> When you get adds they usually are the ones inside the tower. They are hardest to pull because the jump on top of you when they levitate down once you fluxed them.<br>
<br>
Made another run yesterday on specters. With clarity i split up the tower and first pulled the 4 down on the rock. Then med up and pull the 3 on top of the tower and the one inside. <br>
med up and pulled outside again. Went well until another specter group formed and ruined my split. Never had the chance again to pull 4 at the same time so i left. Killed some Greater Spurbones at the pyramid town in the Dreadlands. <p>Branaman Starbinder <Hated Ones > <BR>
48th Dark Elf Wizard on Prexus</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=157.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=63.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=169.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.threadControl?topicID=169.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=169.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=169.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<opt